四名涉事人員在出發前曾合影留念<ref>{{Cite web|author=Palansamy Y|title=Ex-MAS CEO Ahmad Jauhari survives Melawati helicopter crash which killed two|url=https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/08/ex-mas-ceo-ahmad-jauhari-survives-melawati-helicopter-crash-which-killed-tw/1920586|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work={{le|馬來郵報|Malay Mail}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119160429/https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/08/ex-mas-ceo-ahmad-jauhari-survives-melawati-helicopter-crash-which-killed-tw/1920586|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=【直升机空中碰撞】从梳邦机场飞往云顶山脚　途中发生意外 |url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/index.php/news/society/2020/11/08/374166|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-01|work=[[馬來西亞東方日報|東方日報]]|publisher=}}</ref>。上午11時13分，兩架肇事直升機于梳邦蘇丹阿都阿兹沙機場起飛，目的地為[[彭亨州|彭亨州]][[文冬_(马来西亚)|文冬]]的{{le|雲頂山脚|Genting Sempah}}<ref name="Kini">{{Cite web|author=Mohd H|title=Two dead, two injured in Selangor helicopter collision|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/549973|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-08|work=[[當今大馬|當今大馬]]|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119081517/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/549973|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=9M-HCA|url=https://uk.flightaware.com/live/flight/9MHCA/history/20201108/0313Z/WMSA/L%203.21797%20101.75026|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-08|work=FlightAware|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=9M-HCB|url=https://uk.flightaware.com/live/flight/9MHCB/history/20201108/0313Z/WMSA/L%203.21858%20101.74832|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-08|work=FlightAware|publisher=}}</ref>。兩架直升機内各有一名指揮官及一名學員<ref name="HeliHub">{{Cite web|author=|title=08-Nov-20 9M-HCA Guimbal G2 Taman Melawati, Malaysia|url=https://helihub.com/2020/11/08/08-nov-20-9m-hca-guimbal-g2-taman-melawati-malaysia/|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-09|work=HeliHub|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127174222/https://helihub.com/2020/11/08/08-nov-20-9m-hca-guimbal-g2-taman-melawati-malaysia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中藍色直升機載有莫哈末沙比里及莫哈末伊凡，紅色直升機則載有阿末佐哈里及陳彩英<ref name="survivors"/>。當時他們正進行由莫哈末沙比里主導的聯合飛行（{{lang|en|combined flight}}）<ref name="statement">{{Cite web|author=Naz HH|title=My Heli Club: Helicopters flown by experienced pilots|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/640201/my-heli-club-helicopters-flown-experienced-pilots|date=2020-11-11|accessdate=2020-12-04|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111062350/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/640201/my-heli-club-helicopters-flown-experienced-pilots|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩名機師經驗豐富，累積飛行時間均超過7000小時<ref name="7000hrs">{{Cite web|author=黄劲鸿|title=直升机坠毁意外·MY Heli Club全力配合调查|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2374923.html|date=2020-11-11|accessdate=2020-12-04|work=[[星洲日报|星洲日报]]|publisher=}}</ref>。11時28分，兩架直升機調頭，向[[鵝嘜縣|鵝嘜]]方向飛去<ref name="Kini"/>。

11時45分，兩架直升機在美拉華蒂花園上空相撞，當時直升機的飛行高度為約400公尺<ref name="400m"/>。目擊者稱當時紅色直升機撞向飛在前方的藍色直升機，導致該直升機後方被扯落並高速下墜<ref name="eyewitness">{{Cite web|author=Noraina R, Perimbanayagam K|title=Melawati helicopter crash: Eyewitnesses speak to the media|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639331/melawati-helicopter-crash-eyewitnesses-speak-media|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-09|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115538/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639331/melawati-helicopter-crash-eyewitnesses-speak-media|dead-url=no}}</ref>。報導亦稱該直升機其中一扇旋翼折損，並以近乎垂直的角度墜在地面，但避開了附近的幾所公寓。紅色直升機則在空中停留一會兒後成功迫降在附近的{{link-ms|美拉華蒂花園淡米爾小學|Sekolah Jenis Kebangsaan (T) Taman Melawati}}草場<ref name="malaysiaflyingherald">{{Cite web|author=|title=Mid Air Collision Over Melawati|url=https://malaysiaflyingherald.wordpress.com/2020/11/08/mid-air-collision-over-melawati/|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-09|work=malaysiaflyingherald|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043721/https://malaysiaflyingherald.wordpress.com/2020/11/08/mid-air-collision-over-melawati/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==事故後續==

===援救及善後===
雪蘭莪{{le|馬來西亞消防及拯救隊|Fire and Rescue Department of Malaysia|消防及拯救隊}}在11時47分接獲投報，派遣三支拯救隊伍前往援救<ref name="NST">{{Cite web|author=Perimbanayagam K|title=(Updated) 2 killed, 2 hurt in double helicopter crash in Taman Melawati [NSTTV]|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639280/updated-2-killed-2-hurt-double-helicopter-crash-taman-melawati-nsttv|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-08|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113122632/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639280/updated-2-killed-2-hurt-double-helicopter-crash-taman-melawati-nsttv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事發後附近居民趕赴現場查看，發現機上四名人員仍係在座位上，其中紅色直升機陷入草場的軟泥裏，機上兩人傷勢輕微、意識清醒，藍色直升機則損壞不堪，機上兩人當場死亡<ref name="NST"/><ref>{{Cite web|author=Palansamy Y|title=Two helicopters carrying four passengers crash in Melawati, two dead (VIDEO)|url=https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/08/two-helicopters-carrying-four-passengers-crash-in-melawati-two-dead-video/1920566|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-08|work={{le|馬來郵報|Malay Mail}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108062828/https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/08/two-helicopters-carrying-four-passengers-crash-in-melawati-two-dead-video/1920566|dead-url=no}}</ref>。吉隆坡航空救援協調中心（{{lang|en|Kuala Lumpur Aeronautical Rescue Coordination Centre, KL ARCC}}）也獲啓動，即時協調救援行動<ref name="wee">{{Cite web|author=|title=交通部查直升机相撞案，调查报告料30天内出炉|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/550012|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[當今大馬|當今大馬]]|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100358/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/550012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。消拯局與[[馬來西亞皇家警察|警方]]分別在下午一時許證實兩名死者的死訊<ref name="live"/>。由於事故發生地點處於{{le|國際山莊州議席|Bukit Antarabangsa (state constituency)}}轄内，國際山莊州議員兼[[馬來西亞國際貿易及工業部長|馬來西亞國際貿易及工業部長]][[阿兹敏阿里|阿兹敏阿里]]也趕赴現場視察，并要求警方作出深入調查<ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=Azmin urges in-depth investigation into helicopter crash|url=https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/azmin-urges-indepth-investigation-helicopter-crash|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬新社|馬新社]]|publisher={{le|The Edge 財經日報|The Edge (Malaysia)}}|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114310/https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/azmin-urges-indepth-investigation-helicopter-crash|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

民航管理局調查人員與警方科學鑒證組皆在直升機墜毀現場進行調查<ref name="survivors"/>。下午三時，兩名傷者乘坐一輛警車離開事故現場，並拒絕對媒體發言<ref name="survivors"/>。警方稱兩人被送往{{link-ms|安邦醫院|Hospital Ampang}}接受治療<ref name="wreckage">{{Cite web|author=Noraina R |title=Helicopter wreckage sent for investigation|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639353/helicopter-wreckage-sent-investigationa|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-01|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=}}</ref>。下午五時許，飛機殘骸經過約一小時的拆卸程序後被送往梳邦蘇丹阿都阿兹沙機場機庫待進一步調查<ref name="wreckage"/><ref name="AAIB"/>。

===尸體剖驗===
下午1時40分左右，死者的遺體從事故現場移出。起初，遺體據稱將被送往{{le|吉隆坡中央醫院|Kuala Lumpur Hospital}}的國家法醫醫藥機構（{{lang|en|National Institute of Forensic Medicine}}）進行解剖<ref name="Kini"/>，家屬也在接獲消息後趕往醫院<ref name="live">{{Cite web|author=|title=LAPOR LANGSUNG: Helikopter terhempas di Taman Melawati|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/lapor-langsung-helikopter-terhempas-di-taman-melawati-267429|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-01|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108122830/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/lapor-langsung-helikopter-terhempas-di-taman-melawati-267429|dead-url=no}}</ref>。唯下午三時許，該機構發言人稱遺體將送至[[蕉賴|蕉賴]]的{{le|馬來西亞國立大學醫藥中心|Pusat Perubatan Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia}}<ref name="live"/>。

4時23分，兩具遺體送抵國大醫藥中心，該中心隨後發佈文告稱遺體解剖將照[[2019冠狀病毒病馬來西亞疫情|冠病疫情]]期間的[[標準作業程序|標準作業程序]]進行，尸檢因遺體需事先進行[[2019冠狀病毒病|冠病]]的[[2019冠状病毒病检测|快速抗原檢測]]而推遲至次日<ref name="live"/><ref>{{Cite web|author=A FR|title=Melawati chopper crash: Post-mortem only after Covid-19 test results come in|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639368/melawati-chopper-crash-post-mortem-only-after-covid-19-test-results-come|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108141645/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639368/melawati-chopper-crash-post-mortem-only-after-covid-19-test-results-come|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="antigen">{{Cite web|author=Azil F|title=Kronologi tragedi helikopter terhempas di Taman Melawati|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/kronologi-tragedi-helikopter-terhempas-di-taman-melawati-267496|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110105856/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/kronologi-tragedi-helikopter-terhempas-di-taman-melawati-267496|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩名死者的冠病檢測皆呈陰性反應<ref name="sinchew"/>。院方也爲遺體進行[[X光|X光]]及[[電腦斷層掃描|電腦斷層掃描]]，以鑒定死者經受的體内損傷<ref name="antigen"/>。在家屬認尸後<ref name="autopsy">{{Cite web|author=|title=Autopsy report of helicopter crash victims handed to police|url=https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/autopsy-report-helicopter-crash-victims-handed-police|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬新社|馬新社]]|publisher={{le|The Edge 財經日報|The Edge (Malaysia)}}|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109104238/https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/autopsy-report-helicopter-crash-victims-handed-police|dead-url=no}}</ref>，法醫接連為死者莫哈末沙比里及莫哈末伊凡進行剖檢。在事故中受傷的阿末佐哈里及陳彩英也到場慰問家屬，但仍拒絕接受媒體訪問<ref name="sinchew"/>。院方隨後將驗尸報告呈交予警方<ref name="autopsy"/>。

===遺體入土===
驗尸程序在事故發生的隔日完成。前海軍軍官莫哈末沙比里的遺體由[[馬來西亞皇家海軍|馬來西亞皇家海軍]]人員接走，送往[[馬來西亞國防部|馬來西亞國防部]]附近的{{lang|en|Khalid Al-Walid}}[[清真寺|清真寺]]進行祈禱儀式。遺體之後被送往[[峇都喼鎮|峇都喼鎮]]的{{lang|en|Raudhatul Sakinah}}[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]墓地安葬<ref name="laid">{{Cite web|author=Perimbanayagam K|title=Copter crash: Remains of pilot, co-pilot laid to rest|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639553/copter-crash-remains-pilot-co-pilot-laid-rest|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-04|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109074205/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639553/copter-crash-remains-pilot-co-pilot-laid-rest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除家人近親之外，各界友人包括軍中摯友及涉及意外的阿末佐哈里亦有出席<ref>{{Cite web|author=Muhamad H|title=Nahas helikopter Taman Melawati: Allahyarham Mohd Sabri tinggalkan legasi - Panglima TLDM|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/nahas-helikopter-taman-melawati-allahyarham-mohd-sabri-tinggalkan-legasi-panglima-tldm-267595|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-04|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118133919/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/nahas-helikopter-taman-melawati-allahyarham-mohd-sabri-tinggalkan-legasi-panglima-tldm-267595|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

莫哈末伊凡的遺體則由家人接領，送往梳邦{{le|加里爾峰|Puncak Jalil}}的{{lang|en|Al-Ikhwan}}{{le|祈禱室|surau}}進行祈禱儀式，後葬在{{le|梳邦再也UEP區|UEP Subang Jaya|USJ 22}}穆斯林墓地<ref name="laid"/><ref name="TheEdge"/>。家人及摯友均出席觀禮<ref name="TheEdge"/>。

==調查工作==
[[馬來西亞交通部長|馬來西亞交通部長]][[魏家祥|魏家祥]]在事故發生約三小時後發表文告。他稱交通部轄下的{{le|航空事故調查局 (馬來西亞)|Air Accident Investigation Bureau (Malaysia)|航空事故調查局}}已依據[[國際民用航空組織|國際民用航空組織]]發佈的《附件13 - 航空意外及事故調查》（{{lang|en|Annex 13 -  Aircraft Accident and Incident Investigation}}）展開調查工作。參照附件標準，初步調查報告需在事故發生的首三十日内出爐。他亦强調調查主旨并非追責，而是鑒定事發境況及事故肇因，保障人民性命之餘也避免憾事重演<ref name="wee"/>。

事發時馬來西亞大部分地區因冠病疫情而受[[馬來西亞政府|政府]]頒佈的[[2019冠状病毒病马来西亚行动管制令|有條件行動管制令]]約束，政府為遏止疫情散播而禁止民衆進行部分活動<ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=雪隆布CMCO延长至11月9日　为期14天 |url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2020/10/26/371482|date=2020-10-26|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬來西亞東方日報|東方日報]]|publisher=}}</ref>。然而交通部消息指飛行培訓并未被禁，因此飛行活動可按照標準作業程序進行<ref name="cincainews"/>。

事故當午，警方稱將以[[猝死|猝死]]角度調查案件，并已在事發現場向兩名傷者錄供<ref name="wreckage"/>。航空事故調查局則稱次日將傳召兩名傷者協助調查工作<ref name="AAIB">{{Cite web|author=|title=Helicopter collision survivors to be called in to facilitate investigation|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/550039|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬新社|馬新社]]|publisher=[[當今大馬|當今大馬]]|language=|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113185147/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/550039|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9日，警方發表文告表示已向七人錄供，并鑒定另20名證人<ref>{{Cite web|author=|title=Taman Melawati chopper crash: Cops record statements from seven witnesses|url=https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/09/taman-melawati-chopper-crash-cops-record-statements-from-seven-witnesses/1920993|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬新社|馬新社]]|publisher={{le|馬來郵報|Malay Mail}}|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119011642/https://www.malaymail.com/news/malaysia/2020/11/09/taman-melawati-chopper-crash-cops-record-statements-from-seven-witnesses/1920993|dead-url=no}}</ref>；11日，警方再指21名證人已給供，該局也派員前往梳邦機場對直升機殘骸進行調查工作<ref>{{Cite web|author=连俊杰|title=【直升机空中碰撞】警方向21证人录供 |url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/society/2020/11/11/374730|date=2020-11-11|accessdate=2020-12-06|work=[[馬來西亞東方日報|東方日報]]|publisher=}}</ref>。{{lang|en|MY Heli}}俱樂部也在同日發表文告，表示將全力配合有關單位的調查工作<ref name="7000hrs"/>。

==涉事人員==
藍色直升機機師为56歲的莫哈末沙比里，学员则为41歲的莫哈末伊凡，两人皆在意外中喪命。紅色直升機的機師則爲66歲的馬航前首席執行員阿末佐哈里，他和51歲的陳彩英在事件中僅受輕傷<ref name="survivors">{{Cite web|author=Azizah NM|title=Survivors of Melawati chopper accident leave crash site|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639338/survivors-melawati-chopper-accident-leave-crash-site|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-10|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140055/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639338/survivors-melawati-chopper-accident-leave-crash-site|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sinchew">{{Cite web|author=张韦瑜|title=直升机碰撞2死2伤案 | 2死者家属领尸|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2373841.html|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=[[星洲日报|星洲日报]]|publisher=}}</ref>。

莫哈末沙比里生前曾是馬來西亞皇家海軍[[指揮官|指揮官]]，通曉[[德語|德語]]，是一名具經驗的直升機機師，亦是一名出色的泳手。1984年，他獲派前往{{le|德國海軍學院|Mürwik Naval School}}，并在1986年畢業，同年晉升為執行[[少尉|少尉]]。訓練期間，他利用學假及周末空擋考獲私人機師執照。1990年，他在[[柔佛|柔佛]][[居鑾|居鑾]]的[[馬來西亞皇家空軍|馬來西亞皇家空軍]]直升機訓練中心通過了考試，正式成爲一名海軍機師。他繼續在軍中服務，直至20年後退役，并在2010年前往[[中東|中東]]為商業航空公司服務。他同時擁有[[固定翼飛機|固定翼飛機]]及[[旋翼航空器|旋翼航空器]]的飛行駕照。2018年，他成爲了{{lang|en|MY Heli}}俱樂部的首席飛行教官。在家中排名第二的他生前未婚，留下75歲的母親及四個兄弟<ref name="Sabri">{{Cite web|author=David A|title=Melawati chopper crash: 'Mohamed Sabri was a very experienced pilot'|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639311/melawati-chopper-crash-mohamed-sabri-was-very-experienced-pilot|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-10|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122055804/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639311/melawati-chopper-crash-mohamed-sabri-was-very-experienced-pilot|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

莫哈末伊凡生前為一名[[遙感|遙感]]及[[地球空間信息科學|地理空間技術]]專才，在馬來西亞國内[[航空|航空]]、[[航天|航天]]與[[信息及通訊技術|信息及通訊技術]]行業内廣受招攬。他曾幫助政府機構及當地行業掌握遙感及地理空間技術，並擅長運用[[無人航空載具|無人航空載具]]協助航空監測、地圖繪製與收集地理數據<ref name="Irfan"/>。他於2001年完成了[[馬來西亞工藝大學|馬來西亞工藝大學]]的五年遙感[[理學士|學士]]課程，涉身職場數年後成立{{lang|en|IR Technic}}有限公司並擔任首席執行官<ref name="Irfan">{{Cite web|author=David A|title=Chopper crash victim Irfan was remote-sensing, geospatial tech expert|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639805/chopper-crash-victim-irfan-was-remote-sensing-geospatial-tech-expert|date=2020-11-10|accessdate=2020-12-01|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110025840/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/11/639805/chopper-crash-victim-irfan-was-remote-sensing-geospatial-tech-expert|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他生前曾計劃與演員{{link-ms|埃斯瑪·丹尼爾|Esma Daniel}}製作一部關於飛行的電影<ref>{{Cite web|author=Joni F|title=Allahyarham Mohd Irfan rancang untuk buat filem penerbangan - Esma Daniel|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/allahyarham-mohd-irfan-rancang-untuk-buat-filem-penerbangan-esma-daniel-267477|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-10|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115130352/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/allahyarham-mohd-irfan-rancang-untuk-buat-filem-penerbangan-esma-daniel-267477|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=Omar A|title=#Showbiz: Helicopter crash victim Mohd Irfan wanted to produce a flight film|url=https://www.nst.com.my/lifestyle/groove/2020/11/639699/showbiz-helicopter-crash-victim-mohd-irfan-wanted-produce-flight|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-12-06|work={{le|新海峽時報|New Straits Times}}|publisher=}}</ref>。

莫哈末伊凡來自[[吉蘭丹州|吉蘭丹州]]{{le|彭加蘭芝柏|Pengkalan Chepa}}<ref name="laid"/>，從小就對飛行有著濃厚的興趣，并成功取得了飛行執照<ref name="400m">{{Cite web|author=Timbuong J|title=Sayu... abang dedah mesej terakhir Mohd Irfan sebelum nahas|url=https://www.mstar.com.my/lokal/semasa/2020/11/09/sayu-abang-dedah-mesej-terakhir-mohd-irfan-sebelum-nahas|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=mStar|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115184702/https://www.mstar.com.my/lokal/semasa/2020/11/09/sayu-abang-dedah-mesej-terakhir-mohd-irfan-sebelum-nahas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。意外發生時，他連撥九通電話給家人，但家人并未察覺，之後嘗試回電卻無人接聽<ref name="TheEdge">{{Cite web|author=|title=Heli crash victim Mohd Irfan Fikri laid to rest|url=https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/heli-crash-victim-mohd-irfan-fikri-laid-rest|date=2020-11-10|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=[[馬新社|馬新社]]|publisher={{le|The Edge 財經日報|The Edge (Malaysia)}}|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109210736/https://www.theedgemarkets.com/article/heli-crash-victim-mohd-irfan-fikri-laid-rest|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="call">{{Cite web|author=Suhaimi F|title=Ayah 'call' 9 kali, kami tak perasan... - Anak mangsa nahas helikopter terkilan|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/ayah-call-9-kali-kami-tak-perasan-anak-mangsa-nahas-helikopter-terkilan-267627|date=2020-11-09|accessdate=2020-11-10|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109153725/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/ayah-call-9-kali-kami-tak-perasan-anak-mangsa-nahas-helikopter-terkilan-267627|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到墜機照片在社交媒體上傳開，家人通過辨認直升機注冊號及他的手錶，才知曉他發生意外<ref name="TheEdge"/><ref>{{Cite web|author=Muhamad H|title=Nahas helikopter Taman Melawati: Abang tahu adik terlibat nahas daripada gambar tular|url=https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/nahas-helikopter-taman-melawati-abang-tahu-adik-terlibat-nahas-daripada-gambar-tular-267473|date=2020-11-08|accessdate=2020-11-10|work={{le|Astro Awani|Astro Awani}}|publisher=|language=ms|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110040028/https://www.astroawani.com/berita-malaysia/nahas-helikopter-taman-melawati-abang-tahu-adik-terlibat-nahas-daripada-gambar-tular-267473|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在家中排名第四的他留下73歲的母親、九名兄弟姐妹、遺孀及五名孩子<ref name="Irfan"/><ref name="call"/>。

